snippet.title: Girl In Amber full theatrical video (Nick Cave Cover Version Produced by The Flaming Lips)
snippet.description:
Here is the full theatrical version of the video I shot with Alex Hanson of Hipgnosis Media in Fernie BC.

I have another video coming out soon but thought I'd share this one while the new one is getting edited. Hope you like it. :)

Thanks to Wayne Coyne, Michael Ivins, Steven Drozd, Dave Fridmann, Alex Hanson, Adam Laurin, Ross Janzen and Aiden Levesque!

#redhandfiles #nickcaveandthebadseeds #nickcave #flaminglips #theflaminglips
